import * as React from 'react';
import Avatar from '@mui/material/Avatar';
import { Typography } from '@mui/material';
import Box from '@mui/material/Box';
import EmailIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Email';
import Link from '@mui/material/Link';
import WhatsAppIcon from '@mui/icons-material/WhatsApp';
import GitHubIcon from '@mui/icons-material/GitHub';
import LinkedInIcon from '@mui/icons-material/LinkedIn';
import PlaceIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Place';
import Divider from '@mui/material/Divider';

export default function Profile () {
  return (
      <Box sx={{
        display: 'flex',
        alignItems: 'top',
        textAlign: 'center',
        bgcolor: 'black',
        borderRadius: 5,
        color: 'white',
        }}>
          <Box> 
            <Typography sx={{marginTop: 3}} component="h1" variant="h5">
                About Me
            </Typography>
          </Box>

          <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection: 'column',margin:'10px 10px 10px 10px'}}>
          <Divider sx={{bgcolor:'#656565', width:'100%'}} />
            <Box sx={{marginTop: 1, marginBottom: 1, display:'flex', justifyItems:'start', textAlign:'left', alignItems:'center', gap: 1 }}>
              <EmailIcon sx={{width: 30, height: 30}}></EmailIcon>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection:'column'}}>
                <Typography sx={{color:'#8787A3'}} variant="body2">Email</Typography>
                <Link href="mailto:joaolerner@outlook.com.br">joaolerner@outlook.com.br</Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
           
            <Box sx={{marginTop: 1, marginBottom: 1, display:'flex', justifyItems:'start', textAlign:'left', alignItems:'center', gap: 1  }}>
              <GitHubIcon sx={{width: 30, height: 30}}></GitHubIcon>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection:'column'}}>
                <Typography sx={{color:'#8787A3'}} variant="body2">Github</Typography>
                <Link href="https://github.com/joaovictorlernermartins">joaovictorlernermartins</Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
           
            <Box sx={{marginTop: 1, marginBottom: 1, display:'flex', justifyItems:'start', textAlign:'left', alignItems:'center', gap: 1 }}>
              <LinkedInIcon sx={{width: 30, height: 30}}></LinkedInIcon>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection:'column'}}>
                <Typography sx={{color:'#8787A3'}} variant="body2">LinkedIn</Typography>
                <Link href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jo%C3%A3o-victor-lerner-martins-0145a4172/">João Victor Lerner Martins</Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
            
            <Box sx={{marginTop: 1, marginBottom: 1, display:'flex', justifyItems:'start', textAlign:'left', alignItems:'center', gap: 1 }}>
              <WhatsAppIcon sx={{width: 30, height: 30}}></WhatsAppIcon>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection:'column'}}>
                <Typography sx={{color:'#8787A3'}} variant="body2">WhatsApp</Typography>
                <Link href="tel:+5548991695854">+55 (48) 99169-5854</Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
            
            <Box sx={{marginTop: 1, marginBottom: 1, display:'flex', justifyItems:'start', textAlign:'left', alignItems:'center', gap: 1 }}>
              <PlaceIcon sx={{width: 30, height: 30}}></PlaceIcon>
              <Box sx={{display:'flex', flexDirection:'column'}}>
                <Typography sx={{color:'#8787A3'}} variant="body2">Location</Typography>
                <Link href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/9XbxZaXuFTnXPLXR7">Palhoça, Santa Catarina, Brazil</Link>
              </Box>
            </Box>
          </Box>


      </Box>
 
     
  );
}
